  "texts": [
    "We will review some representative deep learning-based methods in the field of polyp segmentation.",
    "CNN-based methods.",
    "Thanks to the development of convolutional neural network (CNN), especially with the introduction of U-Net [20], many models inspired by this architecture have demonstrated promising results.",
    "AC-SNet [25] modifies the skip connections in U-Net into local context extraction modules and adds a global information extraction module.",
    "The features are integrated and then adaptively selected based on a channel attention strategy."
